{"tid":480790,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[淘寶] 品評傳說中比可口可樂更正既「嶗山可樂」!!","createTime":"2017-11-26T13:32:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-02T12:37:01.000Z","uid":75100,"like":19,"dislike":264,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"131341b6fb7cee54976e290b935ea82302a5d2e0","tid":480790,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T13:32:01.000Z","msg":"咩係嶗山可樂??<br />\n<br />\n在正宗嶗山礦泉水的基礎上添加烏棗、白芷、砂仁、良姜、丁香等十餘種中草藥成分和豐富的CO2氣體，採用獨特配方精製而成，是中國青島製造的健康可樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/26/212333_87c4c025cb5b4b8220da40f5709c31f9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F26%2F212333_87c4c025cb5b4b8220da40f5709c31f9.jpg&h=0bc585ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n食評 : <br />\n平時淨係會飲可口可樂原味，因為zero同低糖都有怪味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但飲得多，就覺得可口可樂口味無咩層次，一味死甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/26/212721_186d297b72201b2ecf6c6f91330ada12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F26%2F212721_186d297b72201b2ecf6c6f91330ada12.jpg&h=6681bf79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n倒出黎就咁睇，顏色係同可口可樂一樣既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聞落去，你唔會話覺得好大浸中藥味，有d特別香味咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一飲不得了，有d怪味，諗緊吐唔吐出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但含含下，又覺得幾正，d味道好特別，飲多幾啖會上癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔似可口可樂咁，你好似飲緊化學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可能佢用有氣水整，所以唔會好多泡同氣，無咁易胃漲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n(滿分5★)<br />\n色 : ★★★<br />\n香 :★★★★ ( 本身飲開中藥，唔覺得d味難飲) <br />\n味: ★★★★ ( 如果去食飯，有呢隻可樂, 可口可樂,百事，我會簡呢隻)"},{"pid":"3d05c8a20f2d4054b045b9d071f051277f18f086","tid":480790,"uid":88167,"like":86,"dislike":3,"score":83,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T13:36:00.000Z","msg":"分分鐘仲毒撚過可樂，不了"},{"pid":"d24612b1d3a49f175e93b90298d1d9136cb47fe4","tid":480790,"uid":144,"like":14,"dislike":4,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T13:37:10.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 咩都擺落口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8d39368aa3a1a71e28f495f050347c590d56dc7","tid":480790,"uid":46151,"like":37,"dislike":3,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T13:38:00.000Z","msg":"唔似可口可樂咁，你好似飲緊化學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可樂似化學野<br />\n你支元素週期表都唔似化學嘢咁勁<br />\n果然中國勃起了"},{"pid":"25324abe40bc3a26305390dbeec0df0ff4e919f4","tid":480790,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T13:43:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔似可口可樂咁，你好似飲緊化學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可樂似化學野<br />\n你支元素週期表都唔似化學嘢咁勁<br />\n果然中國勃起了</blockquote><br />\n至少我飲落口清新d，同埋無可口可樂咁漿口同牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 飲落喉嚨幾舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed38f79c84eab8816717655285521189227aec97","tid":480790,"uid":3122,"like":24,"dislike":6,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T13:45:49.000Z","msg":"美國野唔飲<br />\n飲中國野<br />\n中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c29841df8c7f92d97dc4c319d9cd1a51be4baae","tid":480790,"uid":16922,"like":0,"dis