 />\n沙示好好飲喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bef4de1a2de5d92738116a1aac8883382252d57","tid":480790,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T15:14:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>之前係山東行嶗山買過支，沙示d fd嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n沙示好好飲喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n沙示係萬金油味wo ching <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  呢隻比起dr.pepper,沙示正好多...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b5dc4cdf990db29c5856d0cb5e2527f4e32f14a","tid":480790,"uid":60288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T15:21:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>之前係山東行嶗山買過支，沙示d fd嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n沙示好好飲喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n沙示係萬金油味wo ching <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  呢隻比起dr.pepper,沙示正好多...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係黑松沙示喎，係屈臣示、mugs嗰隻<br />\ndr pepper我都麻麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc827b0ea5c927d9498f7dea02ee3d1b7ba50b8f","tid":480790,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T15:23:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>之前係山東行嶗山買過支，沙示d fd嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n沙示好好飲喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n剩係識飲甜野依家D細蚊仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n沙示無返咁上下都唔識得飲"},{"pid":"07b7bf810051fa1518950d78effca07cddb9f057","tid":480790,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T15:27:29.000Z","msg":"想知加咁多中藥材係咪標榜健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"862a5d8e90038a08809d5c6eb5a116605d922553","tid":480790,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T15:29:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想知加咁多中藥材係咪標榜健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n秉承傳統嶗山可樂製作工藝的精華，特別保留了經典的傳統手工炒糖做法，炒出地道十足的中國特有糖香。純正中國糖香融合烏棗的特殊香蘊，嶗山礦泉水的甘冽清香，口感清爽甘甜，滋味獨具一格。<br />\n<br />\n而據中國古醫烏書記載：烏棗性熱，為滋補珍品。良姜性溫、味辛，有健脾暖胃、祛寒燥濕等功效。丁香，辛，溫，歸脾、胃、肺、腎經，溫中降逆，補腎助陽。白芷，散風除濕，通竅止痛。<br />\n<br />\n利申: google <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}